/*
  Blink & Entered all sleep mode

  Turns an LED on for one second, then off for one second, repeatedly.
  Press the IO0 button for entering the sleep mode.

  Most Development Boards have an on-board LED you can control. On the Arduino UNO for the example.
  it is attached to digital pin GPIO 5 the correct LED pin independent of which board is used.
  If you want to know what pin the on-board LED is connected to on your Development Board
  model, check the Technical Specs of your board at:
  https://kmtek.io/
*/
